Lovemap is a tile-based mapping engine for the Love 2d gaming framework (love2d.org) written in Lua.

Lovemap lets you assign different materials, such as dirt, water, grass, etc., to different tiles and handles the rendering of the tiles and their overlays.

Screenshot: http://github.com/joeyschoblaska/lovemap-example/raw/master/screenshot.gif

Example usage: http://github.com/joeyschoblaska/lovemap-example/
